andards and institutional bias against conservatives", "Gavin Newsom as a hypocritical, vulnerable Democratic figure", "Financial disintermediation \u2014 distrust of mainstream banks and institutions"], "threat_level": "medium", "threat_rationale": "The episode aggressively mainstreams a reverse-discrimination framework (''Jim Snow 2.0'') designed to erode public support for DEI and racial equity programs, while preemptively targeting Gavin Newsom ahead of a potential 2028 presidential run \u2014 both narratives with significant base-mobilization potential."}','2026-02-25T06:20:46.494319+00:00',1);
