c support for potential U.S. military action in Mexico, further terrorist designations of cartels with sweeping legal implications, and aggressive immigration crackdowns \u2014 all of which directly threaten progressive immigration policy, diplomatic norms, and civil liberties frameworks."}','2026-02-25T06:20:47.818528+00:00',1);
INSERT INTO episodes VALUES('fe22fdfec07fe6d123f985076b60aea5','War Room (Steve Bannon)','right','Episode 5162: President Trump Honors Angel Moms In  Angel Families Remembrance Ceremony','Mon, 23 Feb 2026 20:56:13 GMT','<span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;">Episode 5162: President Trump Honors Angel Moms In&nbsp;</span><span style="color: rgb(75, 85, 99); font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; background-color: rgb(243, 244, 246);">&nbsp;Angel Families Remembrance Ceremony</span><div><span style="color: rgb(75, 85, 99); font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; background-color: rgb(243, 244, 246);"><br></span></div>','https://chrt.fm/track/5B4639/storage.warroom.org/Episode5162-7cakon6oix.mp3',NULL,'{"synopsis": "In this episode of War Room, Steve Bannon covers President Trump''s Angel Families Remembrance Ceremony, a White House event honoring mothers and families who lost loved ones to crimes committed by undocumented immigrants. The episode uses the ceremony to reinforce the administration''s hardline immigration enforcement narrative, framing it as a moral imperative that Democrats have historically ignored or dismissed.", "key_topics": ["Angel Families Remembrance Ceremony at the White House", "Immigration enforcement and crimes by undocumented immigrants", "Trump administration immigration policy messaging"], "notable_quotes": [{"quote": "President Trump is honoring th